  <source>General Public Hospital Zell am See</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Endoscopic full thickness gastroplication (Plicator-Procedure) has the potential to be a safe
      and effective alternative to laparoscopic antireflux surgery (LARS)to improve symptoms of
      GERD. This prospective randomized study compares objective and subjective outcome parameters
      of Plicator with that of LARS.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
